channel.title: Awesome free MMORPG
channel.description:
I just found this game, that i think you guys will enjoy. [url=http://tale-of-tales.com/TheEndlessForest/]http://tale-of-tales.com/TheEndlessForest/[/url]
Heres a review i did on it [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1DVWSi8_2mw]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1DVWSi8_2mw[/url]
I think you should all try it out, its brilliantly awesome, and i would like to see how people could troll on it (near the end of the video i attempt to give some guy a blow job)
I would also recommend people getting high while playing, as my friend just told me that the game is awesome when you are blazed ;)
